com.github.wuic.nut

Class AbstractNut

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.wuic.nut.AbstractNut
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Nut
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractConvertibleNut, FilePathNut, HttpNut, NutWrapper, WebappNut

    public abstract class AbstractNut
extends Object
implements Nut

    Base implementation of the Nut interface. A Nut is often represented by a name and a NutType. This class already manages it.

    Since:
    0.3.0
    Version:
    1.6
    Author:
    Guillaume DROUET
